pipecat (architecture & API reference)
--------------------------------------
Flowcat is a native-Rust runtime built to the same architecture and public API
model as the pipecat project: the FrameProcessor / Frame taxonomy, the
system-frame priority and interruption model, the service-processor seams
(STT / TTS / LLM / realtime), the carrier serializer set, and the provider
catalogue all follow pipecat's design and interface conventions. Many file-level
doc comments cite the corresponding pipecat source locations for traceability.
pipecat is used as an architecture and API reference; it is licensed under the
